overview: Founded in 2006 and based in beautiful San Diego, California, Sullivan Capital Insurance Services Inc. is focused on helping people manage the risks of everyday life, plan for the future, and recover from the unexpected. Dedicated to providing the highest quality of service, Sullivan Capital Insurance Services Inc. is a group of insurance and financial professionals with expertise in Life Insurance, College Funding, Annuities and Life Settlements.
